LUKE 1.57 iþ Aileisabaiþ usfullnoda mel du bairan jah gabar sunu.
LUKE 1.58 jah hausidedun bisitands jah ganiþjos izos, unte gamikilida frauja armahairtein seina bi izai, jah miþfaginodedun izai.
LUKE 1.59 jah warþ in daga ahtudin, qemun bimaitan þata barn jah haihaitun ina afar namin attins is Zakarian.
LUKE 1.60 jah andhafjandei so aiþei is qaþ:
ne, ak haitaidau Iohannes.
LUKE 1.61 jah qeþun du izai þatei
ni ainshun ist in kunja þeinamma saei haitaidau þamma namin.
LUKE 1.62 gabandwidedun þan attin is, þata ƕaiwa wildedi haitan ina.
LUKE 1.63 iþ is sokjands spilda gamelida qiþands:
Iohannes ist namo is;
jah sildaleikidedun allai.
LUKE 1.64 usluknoda þan munþs is suns jah tuggo is, jah rodida þiuþjands guþ.
LUKE 1.65 jah warþ ana allaim agis þaim bisitandam ina, jah in allai bairgahein Iudaias merida wesun alla þo waurda.
LUKE 1.66 jah galagidedun allai þai hausjandans in hairtin seinamma qiþandans:
ƕa skuli þata barn wairþan?
jah þan handus fraujins was miþ imma.
LUKE 1.67 jah Zakarias, atta is, gafullnoda ahmins weihis jah praufetida jah qaþ:

LUKE 1.68 þiuþeigs frauja guþ Israelis, unte gaweisoda jah gawaurhta uslausein managein seinai, LUKE 1.69 jah urraisida haurn naseinais unsis in garda Daweidis þiumagaus seinis, LUKE 1.70 swaswe rodida þairh munþ weihaize þize fram anastodeinai aiwis praufete seinaize, LUKE 1.71 giban nasein us fijandam unsaraim jah us handau allaize þize hatandane unsis, LUKE 1.72 taujan armahairtiþa bi attam unsaraim jah gamunan triggwos weihaizos seinaizos, LUKE 1.73 aiþis þanei swor wiþra Abraham attan unsarana, ei gebi unsis LUKE 1.74 unagein us handau fijande unsaraize galausidaim skalkinon imma LUKE 1.75 in sunjai jah garaihtein in andwairþja is allans dagans unsarans.
LUKE 1.76 jah þu, barnilo, praufetus hauhistins haitaza;

fauragaggis auk faura andwairþja fraujins, manwjan wigans imma, LUKE 1.77 du giban kunþi naseinais managein is in afleta frawaurhte ize, LUKE 1.78 þairh infeinandein armahairtein gudis unsaris, in þammei gaweisoþ unsara urruns us hauhiþai, LUKE 1.79 gabairhtjan þaim in riqiza jah skadau dauþus sitandam, du garaihtjan fotuns unsarans in wig gawairþjis.
LUKE 1.80 iþ þata barn wohs jah swinþnoda ahmin jah was ana auþidom und dag ustaikneinais seinaizos du Israela.
LUKE 2.1 Warþ þan in dagans jainans, urrann gagrefts fram kaisara Agustau, gameljan allana midjungard.
LUKE 2.2 soh þan gilstrameleins frumista warþ at raginondin Saurim Kwreinaiau.
LUKE 2.3 jah iddjedun allai, ei melidai weseina, ƕarjizuh in seinai baurg.

LUKE 2.4 Urrann þan jah Iosef us Galeilaia, us baurg Nazaraiþ, in Iudaian, in baurg Daweidis sei haitada Beþlaihaim, duþe ei was us garda fadreinais Daweidis, LUKE 2.5 anameljan miþ Mariin sei in fragiftim was imma qeins, wisandein inkilþon.
LUKE 2.6 warþ þan, miþþanei þo wesun jainar, usfullnodedun dagos du bairan izai.
LUKE 2.7 jah gabar sunu seinana þana frumabaur jah biwand ina jah galagida ina in uzetin, unte ni was im rumis in stada þamma.
LUKE 2.8 jah hairdjos wesun in þamma samin landa, þairhwakandans jah witandans wahtwom nahts ufaro hairdai seinai.
LUKE 2.9 iþ aggilus fraujins anaqam ins jah wulþus fraujins biskain ins, jah ohtedun agisa mikilamma.
LUKE 2.10 jah qaþ du im sa aggilus:
ni ogeiþ, unte sai, spillo izwis faheid mikila, sei wairþiþ allai managein, LUKE 2.11 þatei gabaurans ist izwis himma daga nasjands, saei ist Xristus frauja, in baurg Daweidis.
